[01:30.13]Silver dishes for the memories,for the days gone by / 为怀念逝去的日子，我将记忆装在银色的盘子里
[01:35.85]Singing for the promises / 为诺言而歌唱
[01:38.44]Tomorrow may bring / 明天能够到来
[01:40.88]I harbour all the old affection / 我庇护着所有的旧感情
[01:44.31]Roses of the past / 以及曾经的鲜艳玫瑰
