[03:33.00]Everytime you kissed me / 每当你亲吻我的时候
[03:35.51]My heart was in such pain / 我的心像受了重伤
[03:38.82]Gathering the roses / 收集一朵朵玫瑰
[03:41.27]We sang of the grief / 我们唱出忧伤
