[03:47.90]Sweeter than despair / 比绝望更甜美
[03:50.14]We were there, in everlasting bloom / 我们在这里，永恒地绽放着
[03:55.86]Underneath the stars / 在繁星之下
[03:58.44]Shaded by the flowers / 在花影之下
[04:01.46]Kiss me in the summer day gloom, my love / 在夏日的黑暗里亲吻我吧，我的爱
[04:07.23]You are all my pleasure, my hope and my song / 你是我所有的快乐、希望与歌
[04:12.96]I will be here dreaming in the past / 我将于此，在过去中做梦
[04:18.65]Until you come / 直到你出现
[04:21.55]Until we close our eyes / 至死不渝
